1
00:02:34,421 --> 00:02:37,758
Wealth, fame, power.

2
00:02:37,791 --> 00:02:41,295
Gold Roger, the King of
the Pirates, attained this

3
00:02:41,328 --> 00:02:45,132
and everything else
the world had to offer.

4
00:02:45,165 --> 00:02:50,103
And his dying words drove
countless souls to the seas.

5
00:02:50,671 --> 00:02:52,306
You want my treasure?

6
00:02:52,339 --> 00:02:53,407
You can have it!

7
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:56,644
I left everything I gathered
together in one place.

8
00:02:56,677 --> 00:02:59,246
Now you just have to find it!

9
00:02:59,279 --> 00:03:02,483
These words lured men to
the Grand Line in pursuit

10
00:03:02,516 --> 00:03:05,719
of dreams greater than
they've ever dared to imagine!

11
00:03:05,752 --> 00:03:09,122
This is the time known
as the Great Pirate Era!

12
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,562
He escaped from the Hair Bind?

13
00:03:15,863 --> 00:03:17,397
Rumble.

14
00:03:18,165 --> 00:03:21,702
I'm sorry Doctorine. I can't
keep my word.

15
00:03:21,735 --> 00:03:24,538
Maybe I am just like
the Doctor after all.

16
00:03:24,571 --> 00:03:28,108
If he put his life on the
line to save his country,

17
00:03:28,141 --> 00:03:31,611
then I want to put my life on
the line to save my friends.

18
00:03:34,481 --> 00:03:36,350
If I'm going to die anyway.

19
00:03:36,383 --> 00:03:40,588
I have to try it!
Everyone, please stay away.

20
00:03:40,621 --> 00:03:43,056
I'm about to lose control.

21
00:04:03,143 --> 00:04:04,511
"Bubble Master Kalifa!

22
00:04:04,544 --> 00:04:07,013
The Soap Trap
Closes in on Nami!"

23
00:04:14,855 --> 00:04:16,356
Yoyoi.

24
00:04:23,864 --> 00:04:26,634
No one ever informed me
there was a devil fruit

25
00:04:26,667 --> 00:04:30,203
that would actually
turn one into the devil.

26
00:04:30,704 --> 00:04:34,507
But this side of you is
starting to impress me!

27
00:04:37,778 --> 00:04:39,580
Perhaps you are
the devil himself,

28
00:04:39,613 --> 00:04:43,717
or a demon, but a
true man never surrenders,

29
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:44,584
no matter the odds!

30
00:04:44,618 --> 00:04:47,321
On my very honor
as the lion Kumadori,

31
00:04:47,354 --> 00:04:50,658
I'll send you back to the fires
of hell from whence you came!

32
00:04:50,691 --> 00:04:54,061
Mark my words. Shave!

33
00:04:54,094 --> 00:04:56,329
Now! Finger gun Q, Q, Q!

34
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:08,375
Moon Walk!

35
00:05:09,643 --> 00:05:12,012
Shishi Kebab!

36
00:05:27,461 --> 00:05:29,195
Yo. Yoyoi.

37
00:05:29,496 --> 00:05:30,664
You've given me no choice.

38
00:05:30,697 --> 00:05:33,333
With this, you shall fall!

39
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:39,673
