and that guy had number 3.

65
00:07:47,801 --> 00:07:50,204
Well that narrows
things down some.

66
00:07:50,237 --> 00:07:51,305
That can only mean

67
00:07:51,338 --> 00:07:54,275
that secretary lookin'
gal has the number two key.

68
00:07:54,308 --> 00:07:56,343
I better hurry up and find her.

69
00:07:56,376 --> 00:07:59,012
Those guys really need my help.

70
00:08:20,867 --> 00:08:24,538
I was under the impression
that you were short on time.

71
00:08:24,872 --> 00:08:25,773
If that were the case,

72
00:08:25,806 --> 00:08:27,775
it would seem you
aren't trying very hard.

73
00:08:27,808 --> 00:08:30,477
But perhaps this is
all part of your plan.

74
00:08:32,813 --> 00:08:35,816
Don't you mock me.
You'll pay for this!

75
00:08:35,849 --> 00:08:38,452
Sounds great.
I'm ready when you are.

76
00:08:38,485 --> 00:08:40,721
You don't have to
wait for me, y'know?

77
00:08:40,754 --> 00:08:43,657
The battle has already
started, after all.

78
00:08:44,024 --> 00:08:45,492
Arrogant, aren't you?

79
00:08:45,525 --> 00:08:47,161
I mean, you ate a devil fruit.

80
00:08:47,194 --> 00:08:49,663
So that bath is
disabling your power.

81
00:08:49,696 --> 00:08:50,597
If your body's half submerged.

82
00:08:50,630 --> 00:08:53,367
I can't imagine you
can do much damage.

83
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,735
Oh yeah?

84
00:08:54,768 --> 00:08:58,138
You think I'm so cocky
I'd drop my guard?

85
00:09:02,242 --> 00:09:03,577
Don't worry about me.

86
00:09:03,610 --> 00:09:07,047
Even without my powers,
I'm still better off than you.

87
00:09:08,081 --> 00:09:17,791
Pardon me a moment.

88
00:09:17,824 --> 00:09:19,793
Just what the hell
did you do to me?

89
00:09:22,396 --> 00:09:24,698
It would spoil it
if I told you now!

90
00:09:24,731 --> 00:09:26,166
Solving that mystery is part

91
00:09:26,199 --> 00:09:28,435
of the fun of fighting
a power holder.

92
00:09:34,408 --> 00:09:36,210
Whatever it was that
happened to Sanji,

93
00:09:36,243 --> 00:09:39,113
she's obviously the
one who's behind it.

94
00:09:39,146 --> 00:09:40,547
I've gotta be careful.

95
00:09:40,580 --> 00:09:43,116
Otherwise I'll end
up just like him.

96
00:09:46,553 --> 00:09:48,788
I'm finally starting to
get some strength back.

97
00:09:54,394 --> 00:09:56,163
So you think I'm weak, huh?

98
00:09:56,196 --> 00:09:59,099
Well, you haven't seen
the Perfect Clima Tact yet.

99
00:09:59,132 --> 00:10:00,601
If you think I'm
just a pretty face,

100
00:10:00,634 --> 00:10:02,736
you're in for a world of hurt.

101
00:10:06,573 --> 00:10:08,375
I can move my legs.

102
00:10:13,614 --> 00:10:18,151
Here it comes. Thunder Charge!

103
00:10:20,587 --> 00:10:22,122
Swing Arm!

104
00:10:36,169 --> 00:10:38,605
That's an impressive weapon.

105
00:10:42,442 --> 00:10:45,445
Are those clouds?

106
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:49,449
Did you think I'd just lie there
and let you stomp on me?

107
00:10:50,651 --> 00:10:54,354
Here's my Thunder Bolt Tempo!

108
00:11:05,532 --> 00:11:09,269
And that's what happens when
you don't take me seriously.

109
00:11:30,357 --> 00:11:32,693
What an interesting surprise!

110
00:11:32,726 --> 00:11:35,662
I never thought I'd get
struck by lightning indoors.

111
00:11:37,798 --> 00:11:38,866
Damn.

112
00:11:38,899 --> 00:11:41,235
That barrier protected her,
but what was it made of?

113
00:11:41,268 --> 00:11:43,236
It looked like it
turned into bubbles.

114
00:11:43,537 --> 00:11:45,205
You better hurry
and figure that out.

115
00:11:45,238 --> 00:11:48,475
