that--you'll never guess.

117
00:11:51,478 --> 00:11:54,181
It was almost like soap
when you washed it away.

118
00:11:54,214 --> 00:11:56,683
Did you eat some kind
of bubble-bubble fruit?

119
00:11:56,950 --> 00:11:58,785
Is that it?

120
00:12:00,287 --> 00:12:01,188
Well! Still!

121
00:12:01,221 --> 00:12:02,756
Even if you do know
what my power does,

122
00:12:02,789 --> 00:12:05,559
