stronger than me or anything.

123
00:12:05,592 --> 00:12:06,827
Understand?

124
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:09,063
Talk about defensive.

125
00:12:09,096 --> 00:12:11,364
I almost feel bad for her.

126
00:12:11,565 --> 00:12:14,301
To put it one way.
My power is cleanliness.

127
00:12:14,334 --> 00:12:18,105
I'm a soap human thanks
to the Bubble-Bubble fruit.

128
00:12:18,138 --> 00:12:20,740
So my entire body
produces a lather.

129
00:12:22,643 --> 00:12:25,379
Lovely, isn't it?

130
00:12:25,412 --> 00:12:27,381
Whoa. How sexy.

131
00:12:27,414 --> 00:12:29,350
I wish I had a
secretary like her--

132
00:12:29,383 --> 00:12:31,084
wait, I'm talking
like an old man!

133
00:12:31,518 --> 00:12:34,154
Uh. It seems pretty
useless for fighting though!

134
00:12:34,187 --> 00:12:36,056
So, what, do you
make people slip?

135
00:12:36,089 --> 00:12:36,923
The sea of bubbles

136
00:12:36,957 --> 00:12:39,159
that I create obey
my every command.

137
00:12:39,192 --> 00:12:41,261
And I have quite
the imagination!

138
00:12:45,866 --> 00:12:46,834
What the--?

139
00:12:46,867 --> 00:12:48,702
I'll give you an example.

140
00:12:48,735 --> 00:12:50,770
So she wasn't
just taking a bath!

141
00:12:51,137 --> 00:12:55,208
Bubble Master Soap Sheep!

142
00:12:59,212 --> 00:13:00,480
What?

143
00:13:01,581 --> 00:13:03,483
Beautiful, huh?

144
00:13:04,685 --> 00:13:06,820
Yeah, some imagination.

145
00:13:06,853 --> 00:13:10,056
Don't let the fluffy
appearance fool you.

146
00:13:10,690 --> 00:13:15,429
Sheep Cloud Relaxing Bubbles!

147
00:13:15,462 --> 00:13:16,430
Oh. By the way.

148
00:13:16,463 --> 00:13:17,798
Didn't you wonder why
you lost your strength

149
00:13:17,831 --> 00:13:19,500
when you walked in here?

150
00:13:19,533 --> 00:13:21,468
Of course.

151
00:13:21,501 --> 00:13:23,637
That must have had something
to do with her power.

152
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:25,072
What else could it be?

153
00:13:25,105 --> 00:13:26,607
Now that I think about it,

154
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:28,108
when I came through the door.

155
00:13:28,141 --> 00:13:34,147
The floor was
covered with bubbles.

156
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:38,451
Oh, crap!

157
00:13:42,789 --> 00:13:45,659
You took too long
to figure it out.

158
00:13:48,829 --> 00:13:50,764
My strength is fading, again.

159
00:13:50,797 --> 00:13:52,833
It's just like earlier

160
00:13:52,866 --> 00:13:55,068
