that puddle of bubbles.

161
00:13:55,769 --> 00:13:56,870
Give it some time.

162
00:13:56,904 --> 00:14:00,407
You'll soon understand the
true horror of this power.

163
00:14:10,317 --> 00:14:12,253
The bubbles that come
from my body are thorough.

164
00:14:12,286 --> 00:14:14,788
