got locked in the fridge.

211
00:18:39,753 --> 00:18:43,023
That thing's holding
him like a ragdoll.

212
00:18:51,331 --> 00:18:53,500
What the hell did I miss?

213
00:18:59,139 --> 00:19:00,207
That hat.

214
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:03,110
I think it's the same style
that deer was wearing.

215
00:19:03,143 --> 00:19:04,678
Hey! You!

216
00:19:04,711 --> 00:19:07,380
